{"tid":1486793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"求下你地 請聽我講一句！！","createTime":"2019-08-19T03:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:00:11.000Z","uid":27578,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0841421d58ecff00abe573d29e19d938b8b5e5","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:50:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再捉鬼</span><br />\n捉鬼令到你地開始倒退返2014咁<br />\n7月為止我地都冇捉過鬼<br />\n各有各做 文宣既文宣<br />\n和理非既去撐遊行人數<br />\n勇武幫我地衝擊幫我地頂住<br />\n但依排黑警擺到明比你睇有狗混左入去<br />\n你地就自亂陣腳 瘋狂捉鬼<br />\n其實點解唔有得佢地呢？<br />\n我地所有野都可以賴佢地做不失民意<br />\n又有班狗幫我地衝<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而解決驚比佢地cap低既問題</span><br />\n唔好落單 少過一百人就一齊散<br />\n咁樣就算佢地混入黎 都係冇撚用"},{"pid":"e89a395b3a8594d1ff51c1669afef2e70ec5e00d","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"831要人"},{"pid":"7f066a2f5a6df2a31b069a841fd9538f21c73fe3","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"831要人"},{"pid":"1cf06566f5e5644b8f20a7217a5772e621be0af0","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eed0393e8f84503a4b00b1faaa2374dc26a51b8a","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b777ae4fd2e49dea4ff0eed0758dd03ad61b7ec","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dc5a503453f58ea43988a66908df2fe4c82e50e","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1851ec8f15bd35a8f3789df4320bd839177eab44","tid":1486793,"uid":27578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"冇人？"},{"pid":"9e42cf113df9f71b9fe2c3c67ec6d61208508c65","tid":1486793,"uid":44461,"